'''Bantha Music''' is a [[Wikipedia:Music publisher|music publishing]] arm of [[Lucasfilm]]. It is affiliated with [[Wikipedia:BMI|BMI]], and its publishing is administered by Walt Disney Music Publishing.

It is named after the creature called a [[bantha]].

